      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knollcrest%2C_Connecticut"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "That windmill, standing 80 feet tall, houses a 3,000‑gallon copper water tank that still serves the area.",
